{"kanda":6,"sarga":45,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"सतस्यगतिमन्विच्छन्राजपुत्रःप्रतापवान् ।दिदेशातिबलोरामोदशवानरयूथपान्","trans":"Rama, the son of the king, a powerful and strong warrior, ordered ten Vanaras to know the whereabouts (of Indrajith).","words":[{"d":"राजपुत्रः","m":"king's son"},{"d":"प्रतापवान्","m":"powerful"},{"d":"अतिबलः","m":"very strong"},{"d":"सःरामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"गतिम्","m":"where about"},{"d":"अन्विच्छन्","m":"to know"},{"d":"दश","m":"ten"},{"d":"वानरयूथपान्","m":"Vanara troops"},{"d":"दिदेश","m":"assigned."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"द्वौसुषेणस्यदायादौनीलंचप्लवगर्षपम् ।अङ्गदंवालिपुत्रंचशरभंचतरस्विनम् विनतंजाम्बवन्तंचसानुप्रस्थंमहाबलम् ।ऋषभंचर्षभस्कन्थमादिदेशपरन्तपः","trans":"Rama, the scorcher of enemies, ordered the two sons of Sushena, the best of Vanaras Neela, Jambavantha, Angada, as well as courageous Sarabha, Vinatha, and Hanumantha and Sanuprastha endowed with extraordinary might, also Rshaba and Rshaba Skanda.","words":[{"d":"परन्तप","m":"scorcher of enemies"},{"d":"सुषेणस्य","m":"to Sushena"},{"d":"द्वौ","m":"both"},{"d":"दायादौ","m":"Dwivida"},{"d":"प्लवगर्षपम्","m":"best of Vanaras"},{"d":"नीलंच","m":"and Neela"},{"d":"जाम्बवन्तंच","m":"and Jambavantha"},{"d":"अङ्गदम्","m":"Angada"},{"d":"तरस्विनम्","m":"courageous"},{"d":"शरभंच","m":"Sarabha"},{"d":"विनतंच","m":"Vinatha"},{"d":"हनूमन्तम्","m":"Hanumantha"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"mighty strong"},{"d":"सानुप्रस्थम्","m":"Sanuprastha"},{"d":"ऋषभंच","m":"and Rshabam"},{"d":"ऋषभस्कन्धम्","m":"Rshaba Skanda"},{"d":"आदिदेश","m":"ordered."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"द्वौसुषेणस्यदायादौनीलंचप्लवगर्षपम् ।अङ्गदंवालिपुत्रंचशरभंचतरस्विनम् विनतंजाम्बवन्तंचसानुप्रस्थंमहाबलम् ।ऋषभंचर्षभस्कन्थमादिदेशपरन्तपः","trans":"Rama, the scorcher of enemies, ordered the two sons of Sushena, the best of Vanaras Neela, Jambavantha, Angada, as well as courageous Sarabha, Vinatha, and Hanumantha and Sanuprastha endowed with extraordinary might, also Rshaba and Rshaba Skanda.","words":[{"d":"परन्तप"