rows"},{"d":"क्षतविग्रहाः","m":"mangled"},{"d":"भीमवेगाः","m":"endowed with high speed"},{"d":"हरयः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"अन्धकारे","m":"in utter darkness"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him, Indrajith मेघैः cloud"},{"d":"आवृतम्","m":"covered"},{"d":"सूर्यमिव","m":"like Sun"},{"d":"नददृशुः","m":"not seen."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"रामलक्ष्मणयोरेवसर्वदेहभिदश्शरान् ।भृशमावेशयामासरावणिस्समितिञ्जयः","trans":"Indrajith who is ever victorious, pierced repeatedly arrows all over the body of Rama and Lakshmana.","words":[{"d":"समितिञ्जयः","m":"ever victorious"},{"d":"रावणिः","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"सर्वदेहभिदः","m":"all over the body"},{"d":"शरान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"repeatedly"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणयोरेव","m":"on Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"आवेशयामास","m":"pierced."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"निरन्तरशीरीरौतुतावुभौरामलक्ष्मणौ ।क्रुद्धेनेन्द्रजितावीरौपन्नगैश्शरतांगतैः","trans":"Both Rama and Lakshmana were pierced by furious Indrajith with serpents like arrows furious.","words":[{"d":"वीरौ","m":"heroic"},{"d":"तौ","m":"they"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"क्रुद्धेन","m":"furious"},{"d":"इन्द्रजिता","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"शरताम्","m":"with arrows"},{"d":"गतैः","m":"pierced"},{"d":"पन्नगैः","m":"serpents"},{"d":"निरन्तरशरीरौ","m":"all over the body"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"तयोःक्षतजमार्गेणसुस्रावरुधिरंबहु ।तावुभौचप्रकाशेतेपुष्पिताविवकिंशुकौ","trans":"Both Rama and Lakshmana bleeding excessively, wounded profusely, looked bright and red like Kimsuka trees with flowers.","words":[{"d":"तयोः","m":"both of them"},{"d":"क्षतजमार्गेण","m":"wounded profusely"},{"d":"बहु","m":"excessively"},{"d":"रुधिरम्","m":"red with blood"},{"d":"सुस्राव","m":"flowing"},{"d":"तौ","m":"they"},{"d":"उभौ","m":"both"},{"d":"पुष्पितौ","m":"flowery"},{"d":"किंशुकौइव","m":"like Kimsuka trees"},{"d":"प्रकाशितौ","m":"looked bright."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"ततःपर्यन्तरक्ताक्षोभिन्नाञ्जनचयोपमः ।रावणिर्भ्रातरौवाक्यमन्तर्धानगतोऽब्रवीत्","trans":"Then Ravana's son with the corner of his eyes turned red in anger looking like a huge collyrium, vanished from there and spoke these words to the two brothers, Rama, and Lakshmana.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"पर्यन्तरक्ताक्षः","m":"corners of eyes turned red"},{"d":"भिन्नाञ्जनचयोपमः","m":"like a huge collyrium"},{"d":"रावणिः","m":"Ravana's son"},{"d":"अन्तर्धानगतः","m":"vanished"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ","m":"brothers"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"युध्यमानमनालक्षयंशक्रोऽपित्रिदशेश्वरः ।द्रष्टुमासादितुंवापिनशक्तःकिंपुनर्युवाम्","trans":"Indrajith who had fire like eyes, said,\" even the ruler of gods cannot discern while I am fighting war, why speak about you? It is not possible.\"","words":[{"d":"अनालक्षयम्","m":"who has fire like eyes"},{"d":"युध्यमानम्","m":"while fighting war"},{"d":"त्रिदशेश्वरः","m":"Lord of gods"},{"d":"शक्रोऽपि","m":"Indra also"},{"d":"द्रष्टुम्","m":"to see"},{"d":"आसादितुंनापि","m":"cannot discern"},{"d":"नशक्तः","m":"not possible"},{"d":"युवाम्","m":"for you"},{"d":"किंपुनः","m":"why again"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"प्रावृताविषुजालेनराघवौकङ्कपत्रिणा ।एषरोषपरीतात्मानयामियमसादनम्","trans":"\"Raghava brothers! You are enmeshed with plumes of arrows all over the body. My anger will not go waste. I will send you to the abode of Yama, the Lord of death.\"","words":[{"d":"राघवौ","m":"Raghava brothers"},{"d":"कङ्कपत्रिणा","m":"plumes of arrows"},{"d":"शरजालेन","m":"by the fire of arrows"},{"d":"प्रावृतौ","m":"enmeshed"},{"d":"रोषपरीतात्मा","m":"my anger"},{"d":"एषः","m":"in that way"},{"d":"यमसादनम्","m":"to the abode of Lord of death"},{"d":"नयामि","m":"am about to senddispatch you."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वातुधर्मज्ञौभ्रातरौरामलक्ष्मणौ ।निर्बिभेदशितैर्बाणैःप्रजहर्षननादच","trans":"Indrajith having spoken to the righteous brothers Rama and Lakshmana in that way, began to pain them with arrows and stood rejoiced roaring aloud.","words":[{"d":"धर्मज्ञौ","m":"righteous"},{"d":"भ्रातरौ","m":"brothers"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणौ","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having been told"},{"d":"शितैः","m":"stood"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"निर्बिभेद","m":"paining"},{"d":"प्रजहर्ष","m":"rejoiced"},{"d":"ननादच","m":"roaring aloud."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"भिन्नाञ्जनचयश्यामोविष्फार्यविपुलंधनुः ।भूयोभूयश्शरान्घोरान् विससर्जमहामृथे","trans":"Indrajith who was like a mass of crushed black hill, mounting the huge bow released terrific arrows again and again in that great conflict.","words":[{"d":"भिन्नाञ्जनचयश्यामः","m":"like a crushed black hill"},{"d":"विपुलम्","m":"huge"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"विस्फार्यः","m":"mounting"},{"d":"महामृथे","m":"great conflict"},{"d":"भूयोभूय","m":"again and again"},{"d":"घोरान्","m":"terrific"},{"d":"शरान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विससर्ज","m":"released."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"ततोमर्मसुमर्मज्ञोमज्जयननिशितान् शरान् ।रामलक्ष्मणयोर्वीरोननदाचमुहुर्मुहुः","trans":"There after that warrior went on digging sharp arrows into the vital parts of Rama and Lakshmana again and again and kept roaring.","words":[{"d":"मर्मज्ञः","m":"vital"},{"d":"वीरः","m":"warrior"},{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"रामलक्ष्मणयोः","m":"Rama and Lakshmana"},{"d":"मर्मसु","m":"vital parts"},{"d":"निशितान्","m":"sharp"},{"d":"शरान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"मज्जयन्","m":"digging"},{"d":"मुहुर्मुहुः","m":"again and again"},{"d":"ननादच","m":"kept roaring."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"बद्धौतुशरशब्देनतावुभौरणमूर्धनि ।निमेषान्तरमात्रेणनशेकतुदीक्षितुम्","trans":"In a fraction of a second, both Rama and Lakshmana facing the battle were bound by arrows and did not have energy to retaliate.","words":[{"d":"रणमूर्धनि","m":"facing the battle"},{"d":"निमेषान्तरमात्रेण","m":"in a fraction of twinkling of an eye"},{"d":"बद्धौ","m":"bound"},{"d":"तौउभौ","m":"both of them"},{"d":"उदीक्षितुम्","m":"to retaliate"},{"d":"नशेकतुः","m":"not have energy."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"ततोविभिन्नसर्वाङ्गौशरशल्याचितावुभौ ।ध्वजाविवमहेन्द्रस्यरज्जुमुक्तौप्रकम्पितौ तौसम्प्रचलितौवीरौमर्मभेदेनकर्शितौ ।निपेततुर्महेष्वासौजगत्यांजगतीपती","trans":"Pierced all o