efield, their limbs fully covered with arrows, in a highly distressed state.","words":[{"d":"वीरशयने","m":"warrior's bed"},{"d":"शयानौ","m":"bed"},{"d":"रुधिरोक्षितौ","m":"drenched in blood"},{"d":"शरवेष्टितसर्वाङ्गै","m":"all their limbs covered with arrows"},{"d":"परमपीडितौ","m":"highly distressed"},{"d":"तौवीरौ","m":"those warriors"},{"d":"आर्तौ","m":"lying."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"नह्यविद्धंतयोर्गात्रेबभूवाङ्गुळमन्तरम् ।नानिर्भिन्नंनचास्तब्दमाकराग्रादजिह्मगैः","trans":"Not an inch of space on their bodies remained without being pierced. Not even a part of the body was left unshaken, unhurt, or wounded.","words":[{"d":"योः","m":"their"},{"d":"गात्रे","m":"in the body"},{"d":"अविद्धम्","m":"not wounded"},{"d":"अङ्गुळमात्रम्","m":"not even finger breadth space (an inch of space)"},{"d":"अन्तरम्","m":"all over"},{"d":"नबभूव","m":"remained without being pierced"},{"d":"अजिह्मगैः","m":"unhurt"},{"d":"आकराग्रात्","m":"not even a part of the body was left"},{"d":"अनिर्भिन्नम्","m":"not wounded"},{"d":"अस्तब्दम्","m":"unshaken"},{"d":"न","m":"not."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"तौतुक्रूरेणनिहतौरक्षसाकामरूपिणा ।असृक्सुस्रुवतुस्तीव्रंजलंप्रस्रवणाविव","trans":"Wounded by the cruel Rakshasas capable of changing form at their will, blood flowed from their body copiously like water from spring bringing out their vital life breaths.","words":[{"d":"क्रूरेण","m":"by the cruel"},{"d":"कामरूपिणा","m":"capable of acquiring desired form"},{"d":"रक्षसा","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"निहतौ","m":"wounded"},{"d":"तौ","m":"both"},{"d":"प्रस्रवणौ","m":"flowed"},{"d":"जलम् इव","m":"like water"},{"d":"तीव्रम्","m":"copiously"},{"d":"असृक्","m":"vital breaths"},{"d":"सुस्रुवतुः","m":"brought forth."}]},{"v":22,"dev":"पपातप्रथमंरामोविद्धोमर्मसुमार्गणैः ।क्रोधादिन्द्रजितायेनपुराशक्रोविनिर्जितः","trans":"Rama fell first pierced by arrows in his vital parts released in anger by Indrajith, by whom Indra was utterly defeated.","words":[{"d":"येन","m":"by whom"},{"d":"पुरा","m":"earlier"},{"d":"शक्रः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"वि